cancellation_policy: For cancellation, no penalty till 1 hour before departure & 100% penalty beyond that.

For cancellation, please visit the MyTrips Section on the app/website or use the link shared with you in booking confirmation SMS. In case of any issue regarding cancellation, please call our support team at 0124 4628747, 0124 5045105
MakeMyTrip(MMT) will not be held responsible for any cancellation or delay of service in case of any natural calamity, agitation or strike, traffic jam or road blockage, etc.
In the event of cancellation of a cab trip, MMT's liability will be limited only to the extent of refunding the sum paid by the passenger for the price of the e-ticket
